<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URL Redirect Notice</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #4f46e5;
            --primary-hover: #4338ca;
            --background-start: #e0e7ff;
            --background-end: #c7d2fe;
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, var(--background-start), var(--background-end));
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 32rem;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .icon-container {
            width: 4rem;
            height: 4rem;
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
        }
        .icon {
            width: 2rem;
            height: 2rem;
            fill: var(--primary-color);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.875rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .url-info {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .url-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .url {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .arrow-icon {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
        .arrow-icon svg {
            width: 1.5rem;
            height: 1.5rem;
            fill: var(--primary-color);
            animation: bounce 1s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }
        .button-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }
        .button-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-hover);
        }
        .button-secondary {
            background-color: white;
            color: #374151;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        }
        .button-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .buttons {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <div class="icon-container">
                <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M5 13h11.86l-3.63 4.36a1 1 0 0 0 1.54 1.28l5-6a1.19 1.19 0 0 0 .09-.15c0-.05.05-.08.07-.13A1 1 0 0 0 20 12a1 1 0 0 0-.07-.36c0-.05-.05-.08-.07-.13a1.19 1.19 0 0 0-.09-.15l-5-6A1 1 0 0 0 14 5a1 1 0 0 0-.64.23 1 1 0 0 0-.13 1.41L16.86 11H5a1 1 0 0 0 0 2z"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>URL Redirect Notice</h1>
            <p>You are about to be redirected to a new URL. Please review the destination before proceeding.</p>
            <div class="url-info">
                <p class="url-label">Current URL:</p>
                <p class="url"><script>document.write(location)</script></p>
                <div class="arrow-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M12 5v14M19 12l-7 7-7-7"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="url-label">Destination URL:</p>
                <p class="url"><%= url %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="<%= url %>" class="button button-primary">
                    Proceed to New URL
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon" style="width: 1rem; height: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;">
                        <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path>
                        <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline>
                        <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line>
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="button button-secondary">Go Back</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If there is any abuse, please report it to <a href="mailto:abuse@qurl.us.kg">abuse@qurl.us.kg</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>